version_description: This song does not really have full chords, so these are approximations. Please watch the youtube tutorial I linked for playing instructions.
The other two tabs were slightly off in their chords and lyrics so I corrected them.
This has all of the chords in the original key.
Other version was capo III and this is an open chord version based off of Ben Gibbard playing this for NPRs tiny desk concert.
The previous four versions are either partly incorrect or do not include all of the parts. This version is completely correct and complete as well.
